# this is the main prompt, everything starts here.
-----

Defines

#root_dir = ../

Instructions
1. Initialize the git directory at #root_dir if not yet set.
2. Create a script in the ../setup folder that to setup the virtual environment in the #root_dir
3. Create a file named requirements.txt , this will contain a list of packages need by the application.
4. Create a script in the ../setup folder that will install the needed packages found in the ../requirements.txt
